3.0.0-rc2.name: drupal/tripal_phylogeny

security-coverage.message: RC releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

3.0.0-rc2.description: Supports the phylogeny tables of Chado by providing pages for viewing and editing of phylotrees. Table list at: http://gmod.org/wiki/chado_phylotree_Module. This module was added to Tripal through collaboration with the LegumeInformation group (http://http://legumeinfo.org/)
